{
  "stem": "25773.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "She was married to a non-Jew, to a Polish officer, who was skilled in cutting, which is very well-known story.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "All the Polish officers were killed by the Russians in cutting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And she was in this organization as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And she give me shelter till my papers would come through.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And as, you know, my luck would come, all along like it would be a certain break in my luck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I went one day to the place adjoining to the old ghetto, which was burnt out already and all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And I was walking the street, and then I, you know, [INAUDIBLE] and think about what happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And, you know, being complete like in a daze, it was the first time that I dared to go there, near that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And I didn't-- just opposite past the window-- it was a big, big, big, window, shop window.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I looked into this window, watching the things there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And a young girl approached, looked into this window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And then we looked at each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And I mean, it is unbelievable to believe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "But it really happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And I met my friend Marsha Garfinkel, who was in the same school, a class higher.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It really happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, it was like my providence was guiding things for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like my prov-- whatever it might be up there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I certainly am grateful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, oh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- it was, you know, you can imagine the enthusiasm and the embracing and the outpouring of news and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, her whole family was saved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Her three sisters worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They all-- because when the ghetto started, her cousin, to whom she was engaged, was a very clever man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was an agriculture engineer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was very clever.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
